{
  "stem": "3085.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But-- we were hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were very hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we weren't starving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We, we did lose a lot of weight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But that wasn't-- we were still better off, I think, than most people in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, as far as the-- what we were doing, what was done to us, again, my brother and I, I think, were lucky, maybe because we were at the tail end of this-- the group.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We weren't experimented on to the same extent and some-- as some of the others.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I recall-- obviously I don't recall everything that was done.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The, the, the routine used to be that what-- Mengele would pick a pair of twins and have them transported to his office or his, his, his lab or whatever.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he would do experiments on that pair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then they would go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then-- and then the next day or next week or whatever, another pair.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, I, I-- his experiments-- I, I mean, I-- [SIGHS] in retrospect, they were really phony.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, I, I, I understand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'm not certainly not a medical doctor, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But, but as I understand it, they were-- they were-- they didn't have much scientific value.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That's my understanding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But, of course, at that time, I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Most of the time, when we were called and taken to his office, we were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they took blood from us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "A number of-- I must have had six or seven times they took blood from me and my brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I can't remember how much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I have, of course, no idea why-- what he did with the blood.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
